叫中型舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你做左幾耐咩，起到9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab9398ac84f4bc566a9efa12a572c81c39caba","tid":22491,"uid":13277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢呢排請pt夜更<br />\n有咩做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇做咩dept，如果做food都係上貨tidy up同收錢，賣衫嗰邊都係企下fitting，收錢，tidy up同serve客攞size同幫客check貨<br />\n不過pt人工嚟講馬莎算出手高62蚊一個鐘<br />\n<br />\n利申港島閪鋪pt</blockquote><br />\nwait $62/hr咁高?<br />\n如果想入而做賣衫sales係咪應該直接walk in?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPT 咩 dept 都要做<br />\n而家walk in 應該無咩鋪頭得閒in 你 聖誕peak period<br />\n睇下過左聖誕去in lu"},{"pid":"f218243be3bb3b0abd02836799716f50323ae3cd","tid":22491,"uid":17523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢呢排請pt夜更<br />\n有咩做？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇做咩dept，如果做food都係上貨tidy up同收錢，賣衫嗰邊都係企下fitting，收錢，tidy up同serve客攞size同幫客check貨<br />\n不過pt人工嚟講馬莎算出手高62蚊一個鐘<br />\n<br />\n利申港島閪鋪pt</blockquote><br />\nwait $62/hr咁高?<br />\n如果想入而做賣衫sales係咪應該直接walk in?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有2個方法apply一個係send cv去hr，<br />\n第二個係直接落鋪in，<br />\n不過而家大多數請嘅都係food pt，<br />\n因為而家focus喺food嗰邊多所以會要多啲人尤其是係男仔。<br />\n如果真係淨係想去賣衫嗰邊嘅見嗰陣可以同經理講，<br />\n如果唔係嘅佢地邊個dept唔夠人就會編你過去"},{"pid":"606290ff8ec2b4e38e718a731dc6785205df49e7","tid":22491,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:06:36.000Z","msg":"仲未有D真正名店Sales出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no